channel.title: Completed Content - May consider releasing some code in the future
channel.description:
Decided that since I am not wanting to run my own server, but still program, I am going to code small things that will eventually pile in. This is just content, nothing special like rewriting a core. I will keep a list of updates below on what I am currently doing and will post pictures. This is all being programmed on a PI source. imsuperman05 and I will be developing on this source to release code and some will be off limits to people.
[b][size=14pt]Currently being Worked on[/size][/b] Price Checking Completly rethinking and rewriting Slayer
